content:
The White House

President Obama to Travel to Scranton, Pennslyvania





	WASHINGTON, DC â€“ On Wednesday, November 30th, President Obama will travel to Scranton, Pennsylvania where he will discuss the American Jobs Act. In the evening, the President will travel to New York City where he will attend campaign events. More details will be released when they become available.
